<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1039099" n="1"/> 
  <opener>Ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-1012090132" type="person">Andream Ritsium</rs>, <rs key="place_GEO-2658822" type="place">Sangallum</rs>.</opener>
  <p><lb/>Est quod et Tibi gratuler de felici tuo <rs key="place_GEO-2658822" type="place">Sangallum</rs> adventu, et mihi de propensa tua in me voluntate,
  <lb/>quam tam luculentis Amiciti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> testimoniis hactenus mihi probatam dedisti. Grates quas agis pro exhibitis
  <lb/>tibi <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me officiis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tamen pauca admodum esse scio, in sinum tuum refundo, et vicissim gratias, quas
  <lb/>pro favore et amore tuo tibi debeo, non tam verbis persolvo, quam <add>in</add> continuo tibi inserviendi studio pa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ratas sisto, quod ut ulteriori verborum ambage tibi demonstrem supervacuum esse judico, qualis
  <lb/>enim sit animus erga te meus satis ut puto nosti, quemadmodum et ego de amicitia tua, quam
  <lb/>nec inane nomen esse nec futuram spero, sum persuasissimus. Sex illos florenos <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>Dno</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-104222069" type="person">Im Hof</rs>
  <lb/>acceptos pro te <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs> meo exsolvi, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pecuni<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a ideo solvenda fuit, quia non pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sens,
  <lb/>uti alias requiritur, sed absens promoveberis, pro quo privilegio in superioribus Facultatibus
  <lb/>duplum ordinari<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> exposcunt; imo etiam ipse Doctor <rs key="pers_DE-588-118088440" type="person">Wollebius</rs>, quem procul dubio bene
  <lb/>nosti, et qui sub camino titulo Magisterii insignitus fuit, Facultati Philosophic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> 18 Imperiales
  <lb/>persolvere debuit; memini etiam te ipsum <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>nisi fallor<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> de 18 Imperialibus et de sex florenis lo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cutum fuisse, quin et illud quod <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> meus ultra su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>am jam expensam nihil amplius
  <lb/>requiri dixerit, quod tamen ille, ut facile conjicere potui et ipse mihi fassus est, de ordinariis
  <lb/>sumtibus non cogitans de extraordinariis intellexit. Solutionem igitur eo minus etiam distuli,
  <lb/>quoniam tentaminis tibi facta est gratia, et metuendum erat, ne <rs type="person">Promotor</rs>, nisi pecunia solve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>retur, nomen tuum in <rs type="biblio">Progra<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ate</rs> omitteret, cum <choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> contra hic tibi jam continget honor, quod
  <lb/>primo loco inter <rs type="person">Candidatos</rs> etiam ante illos, qui jam ante semestre examinati et admissi fue<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>runt, collocaberis. <date>Heri</date> trium <rs type="person">Zwingerorum</rs> promotio celebrata fuit, quam vestra brevi se<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quetur. Privilegia Magistrorum, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tibi perscribi cupis, consistunt, quantum quidem scio, in ju<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re superiorem cathedram conscendendi, in publicis disputationibus pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sidendi, tecto capite opponen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>di, liberales artes docendi, aureos a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>ulos gestandi, apud nos quoque collegia privata instituere
  <lb/>aut ad Professionem Philosophicam aspirare nemini licet nisi Doctoribus Philosohi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sive <abbr>L. A.</abbr>
  <lb/>Magistris. Alia privilegia, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quidem alicujus momenti sint, non scio, nisi et hoc inter
  <lb/>privilegia Magistrorum velis numerare, quod Magister possit magister bibere, sed cum
  <lb/>hoc jure et alii utantur, vides quid de illo sentiendum sit. Qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> de <rs type="biblio">catalogo mortuorum</rs>
  <pb facs="1039100" n="2"/>
  <lb/>coram locutus sum, ea breviter huc redeunt, quod scire vellem quoto quisque <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tatis su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>o ex om<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nibus illis, qui eodem a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>o nati sunt, iterum denatus sit, in quem finem <rs type="biblio">catalogus</rs> in hunc mo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dum confici potest; ubi, ut vides, tales a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>i seligi debent,
  <lb/>ut nemo eorum, qui illis annis lucem primum viderunt,
  <lb/>amplius superstes esse possit. Ignosce autem qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so,
  <lb/>Amice charissime, quod tam libere tecum ago, et tibi
  <lb/>nedum aliis laborem hunc impono, tribuas hoc velim
  <lb/>Amiciti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, cujus intuitu et ego ad qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>libet
  <lb/>officia me tibi paratissimum esse spondeo. Vale. <!-- bis hier kollationiert -->
</p>
